Text.string: Don't worry. I ain't a cannibal.
Hey. Got any spare change?
Dollar for a dance? Dollar for a dance!
Heya, Vault Hunter!
A Vault Hunter!
Hi, do you have any sunblock or fresh skin you're not using?
Hello! I am sweaty!
Can't sleep, that's when THEY come.
A Vault Hunter! Yes, yes! Protect me from night terrors!
Can you hear them? They won't leave me alone.
Oh, there you are. Was I talking to myself again?
Don't tickle me, okay? Like, if you were thinking about it, please don't. I've been through enough.
Honestly, I'm as surprised as anyone that I've survived this long.
Oh, you're talking to me. Thanks. That's nice of you.
Don't mind me. I'm fine. Probably fine.
Have you heard about Azlan DeVega's secret stash? No? Me neither, heh-heh-heh.
What, me? I'm fine. Why do you ask?
I heard the Calypsos aren't from Pandora. They're not even bandits, but they RULE the bandits. Does that make... any sense to you?
People just want something to believe in. Even if it's a lie. That's why the COV caught fire.
The Children of the Vault started on Pandora, but it could've happened anywhere. That's the scary thing.
Fine. I'm a coward! There, I said it! Are you happy now?!
Do you think the Great Vault is real?
When I fall asleep, I dream of Tyreen Calypso... And not in the good way.
If you'll excuse me, I'm kind of in the middle of something here.
Is it the ship? Is Sanctuary speaking to me?
Never thought I'd be aboard a genuine space craft.
Oh, me? I'm just... on a space ship. You know how it goes.
Soaring through spaaace, spaaace, spaaace... heh, sorry.
At least I'm not the only weirdo on this ship. It's starting to feel like home, even.
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
You'll be back!
You haven't seen the last of me!
Bye for now, friend!
You'll be sorry!
Bye!
Talk to you later, VH!
See ya around, I guess.
Was it something I said?
Did I make a social error? If so, let me know! It's the only way I'll learn.
May the wind guide your journey!
No! I already told you, I'm not doing that.
Guhh, shut up, SHUT UP!
Why am I sticky? I hate being sticky.
Bored! Why won't someone give me a mission?
[yawn] Sleepy. What a rager, though! Good times.
Rgh. Grrr. Rgrhrgh.||—Agh, I'll never learn skag!
WHY WON'T ANYONE LISTEN TO ME? I'M SCREAMING AS LOUD AS I CAN!
Get out of my head!
You will do no such thing. You hear me?
Stop telling me to do things!
You're not the boss of me!
Because it's a little bus, that's why!
Leave me alone!
I'm unemployed and ANGRY!
I'm not arguing with you. I'm AGREEING with you.
Oh, heck yeah!
Dude! You rock!
Oh, man. Amazing!
Woohoo! Yeah!
Unbelievable!
You are the best!
You Vault Hunters rule!
Big fan of your work!
Way to kick some ass!
[burp] Tastes like skag.
[burp] Oh, really shouldn't have eaten that.
[burp] I'm gonna be feeling that one later.
Hey, remember me?
Still over here.
I know you!
Nice day for a fight!
Happy to be on board.
Ahoy there!
